---
title: Grilled Turkish-Inspired Pork Chops with Grilled Veggie Tabouleh and Lemon-Feta Sauce
description: Pork chops just taste better grilled! Fragrant Turkish-style spice blend, pork and a colourful grilled veggie tabouleh are a perfect match! Topped with a creamy, lemony feta sauce, this dish is summer at its best!
